      `<i>min kókótire ngo ató</i><br>Where the kokotire crocodile lies on the water`,
      `<i>mãna nhiok kóré kuman ibô ne</i><br>With side warming up`,
      `<i>eae eae eae gu ga</i><br>Nhiok goes bathing with her head bent`
